    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><em>Greeting: \"The frigid veil persists.\" | Response: \"All the world in winter's white.\" | Parting: \"May her blessing chill you.\"</em></p><p>Traveling priestesses who move between all Ten-Towns settlements conducting rituals on holy days, maintaining temples and shrines, and pressuring town leaders to perform humanoid sacrifices. Only icebringers and above know the location of Solstice Island. They create and bestow black ice rings to darkhands. Spellcasting: 9th-level, save DC 16, +8. Note: AC 16 with coldskin active.</p><p><strong>Renown 50 | CR 6</strong></p>"
